f\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":42004,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2024\/07\/21\/celebrity-imams\/","url_meta":{"origin":18865,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Celebrity: Wealth and status dangerous like wolves","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 21, 2024","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cTwo ferocious wolves in a pen of sheep, devouring and destroying, are not as harmful than the love of high status and wealth are to the religion of a Muslim.\u201d Source: Musnad al-Bazza\u0304r 6192 Grade: Sahih\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5171,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/15\/trial-of-ummah-wealth\/","url_meta":{"origin":18865,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Wealth: Trial of the Muslim nation is its wealth","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 15, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ka\u2019b ibn 'Iyad reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, every nation has a trial, and the trial of my nation is wealth.\u201d Source:\u00a0Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2336 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0643\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0628\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0627\u0636\u064d \u0642\u